Ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 un-tian2 e7, u7-si5 ia7 u7 iu-chhiu5 lim5-kau3, chiaN5-choe3 lan2 oah8-mia7 e5 li7-ek.  Iu-chhiu5 m7-si7 khoa3-lu7, iu-chhiu5 siong5 oe7 chhoa7 lan2 jip8 khah chhim khah koan5 e5 sou2-chai7.  Iu-chhiu5 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 le5-thau5, le5 kau3 chhim e5 sou2-chai7 chiu7 oe7 kiat-chhut choe7-choe7 koe2-chi2.  Lan2 na7 m7-bat tui7-loh8, lan2 chiu7 bo5 su-iau3 iu-chhiu5, lan2 chi2 su-iau3 siok8-thian e5 hi2-lok8 kou2-le7 lan2 chin3-jip8 khah chhim; chong2-si7 lan2 bat tui7-loh8, lan2 chiu7 iau3 iu-chhiu5 toa3-nia2 lan2 seng2-chhat, thong3-hoe2, jim7-sek ka-ki7.  Sou2-i2 iu-chhiu5 oe7 hou7 lan2 to su-siuN2, to kho2-lu7.  KiN3-na7 Siong7-te3 sou2 toa7-eng7 e5 lang5, long2 keng-koe3 iu-chhiu5.  Iok-sek pi2 ki5-u5 e5 hiaN-ti7 iu-chhiu5 khah choe7, Siong7-te3 eng7 i chin2-kiu3 I2-sek-liat8 choan5-ke kap ki5-thaN bin5-chok8. Tai7-pit8 kap Po2-lo5 ia7 long2 keng-koe3 chin-choe7 iu-chhiu5.  Lan2 e5 Chu2 ui7 lan2 e5 ian5-kou3 ia7 chhi3-koe3 iu-chhiu5, Seng3-keng chheng I choe3 “Iu-chhiu5 e5 kiaN2”.  Siong7-te3 siong5 li7-iong7 iu-chhiu5 khi3 hun3-lian7 i e5 pok8-jin5.  Lan2 oe7-thang kong2: “Am3-mi5 si7 u7 hok e5, in-ui7 am3-mi5 u7 chhiN”.  Lan2 ia7 thang kong2: “Iu-chhiu5 si7 u7 hok e5, in-ui7 iu-chhiu5 lai7-bin7 u7 Siong7-te3 e5 an-ui3.”                         Siok8-thian e5 oah8-mia7.       
